she can't change her cheap,

557
00:23:52,119 --> 00:23:53,359
frugal ways ingrained in her.

558
00:23:53,800 --> 00:23:54,439
Sending such

559
00:23:54,439 --> 00:23:55,599
embarrassing items here!

560
00:23:56,760 --> 00:23:58,040
My son.

561
00:23:58,040 --> 00:24:00,119
You must do well for us.

562
00:24:01,119 --> 00:24:03,000
Pass as a candidate and come back.

563
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:04,199
Then in the future,

564
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:05,160
no one can

565
00:24:05,160 --> 00:24:06,719
block the three of us.

566
00:24:07,479 --> 00:24:08,959
Mother, just rest assured.

567
00:24:09,760 --> 00:24:11,319
Scholar Zhuang even said

568
00:24:11,800 --> 00:24:13,079
that at my age,

569
00:24:13,199 --> 00:24:14,439
to be able to

570
00:24:14,439 --> 00:24:15,560
write such essays was not easy.

571
00:24:16,640 --> 00:24:17,239
Many examples

572
00:24:17,239 --> 00:24:18,760
of much older men

573
00:24:18,880 --> 00:24:19,920
still lack compared to

574
00:24:19,959 --> 00:24:21,119
my knowledge and composition vigor.

575
00:24:22,199 --> 00:24:23,079
Also, even if

576
00:24:23,079 --> 00:24:24,319
I actually don't pass,

577
00:24:24,599 --> 00:24:26,439
I have so many acquaintances all this time.

578
00:24:27,000 --> 00:24:28,400
Heirs of grand aristocrats.

579
00:24:28,520 --> 00:24:29,760
So I won't need to worry about not having a connection.

580
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:31,479
You're not allowed to speak nonsense.

581
00:24:31,520 --> 00:24:32,760
You've got the big exam tomorrow.

582
00:24:32,760 --> 00:24:33,920
Don't speak ominous words. Alright?

583
00:24:46,959 --> 00:24:48,800
Miss.

584
00:24:48,800 --> 00:24:51,400
Weirui Balcony and Linqi Pavilion are in total chaos.

585
00:24:51,560 --> 00:24:53,160
More bustling than a family that's moving.

586
00:24:53,680 --> 00:24:55,040
Big Madam and Mistress Lin

587
00:24:55,040 --> 00:24:56,079
would love to just drag the storage

588
00:24:56,119 --> 00:24:56,959
to the exam yard if they could.

589
00:24:57,719 --> 00:24:59,119
I keep getting called

590
00:24:59,119 --> 00:25:00,359
to help with getting stuff.

591
00:25:00,479 --> 00:25:01,479
I'm exhausted.

592
00:25:03,000 --> 00:25:04,839
But don't ever call out your exhaustion in front of others,

593
00:25:05,599 --> 00:25:08,239
or your exertion will get you no points.

594
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:10,880
Yes.

595
00:25:11,479 --> 00:25:12,199
By the way,

596
00:25:12,199 --> 00:25:14,400
Young Lord is going to the exam tomorrow too?

597
00:25:17,280 --> 00:25:18,119
Miss?

598
00:25:20,599 --> 00:25:21,439
Miss?

599
00:25:23,520 --> 00:25:25,760
He...So what if he does.

600
00:25:25,760 --> 00:25:26,719
It has nothing to do with me.

601
00:25:29,479 --> 00:25:30,560
Miss!

602
00:25:31,880 --> 00:25:33,560
The Young Lord from Duke Qi Manor is here.

603
00:25:34,119 --> 00:25:35,199
Saying since he's studied so much

604
00:25:35,199 --> 00:25:37,800
at our home academy all these years,

605
00:25:38,040 --> 00:25:39,319
he came especially to show his gratitude.

606
00:25:39,880 --> 00:25:41,199
He brought gifts for

607
00:25:41,199 --> 00:25:42,359
each of the Young Masters and Misses,

608
00:25:42,359 --> 00:25:43,599
delivered to each room.

609
00:25:46,280 --> 00:25:47,199
Miss.

610
00:25:47,199 --> 00:25:49,439
This was brought here by Buwei personally.

611
00:25:49,800 --> 00:25:51,199
He said when the Young Lord sent him

612
00:25:51,199 --> 00:25:53,439
to purchase items for the Imperial exam,

613
00:25:53,880 --> 00:25:55,640
he had him procure a nice brush for you.

614
00:25:57,640 --> 00:25:58,400
And there are other

615
00:25:58,400 --> 00:25:59,400
little things here,

616
00:25:59,680 --> 00:26:00,800
to have you pick out all you want.

617
00:26:03,280 --> 00:26:04,319
Buwei also said,

618
00:26:04,319 --> 00:26:05,280
no one else had

619
00:26:05,560 --> 00:26:06,959
this purple hare brush.

620
00:26:13,239 --> 00:26:14,839
Where is the Young Lord right now?

621
00:26:16,800 --> 00:26:18,439
He went to pay visit to Master

622
00:26:18,439 --> 00:26:19,839
and now he should be at Old Madam's room.

623
00:26:21,640 --> 00:26:25,119
Miss, maybe we sneak out and take a look?

624
00:26:25,760 --> 00:26:26,800
Look at what?

625
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:29,479
He's taking the exam tomorrow. Don't distract him.

626
00:26:32,160 --> 00:26:33,479
There are too many items

627
00:26:33,479 --> 00:26:34,760
and I can't take them all.

628
00:26:35,239 --> 00:26:36,400
I'll just pick out

629
00:26:36,400 --> 00:26:37,719
a few to honor his good will.

630
00:26:38,520 --> 00:26:39,760
The rest,

631
00:26:39,760 --> 00:26:41,000
let's have him take them back.

632
00:26:42,000 --> 00:26:42,959
You two go out first

633
00:26:42,959 --> 00:26:44,319
and thank Buwei for me.

634
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:46,400
Alright.

635
00:26:46,400 --> 00:26:47,079
Let's go, Xiaotao.

636
00:27:42,640 --> 00:27:44,199
May you pass the exam quickly,

637
00:27:44,199 --> 00:27:44,719
to put to good use the exertion

638
00:27:44,719 --> 00:27:45,800
you've put in these years.

639
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:49,119
Afterwards.

640
00:27:51,359 --> 00:27:52,000
Thanks.

641
00:28:01,000 --> 00:28:03,959
Second Son! Second Son!

642
00:28:04,680 --> 00:28:06,800
It's so late, but you're still going out?

643
00:28:06,959 --> 00:28:08,719
You might get a cold.

644
00:28:08,719 --> 00:28:10,680
You're going to the exam yard tomorrow.

645
00:28:12,000 --> 00:28:14,439
Tonight, just stay home and rest.

646
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:16,280
Whatever you need tomorrow,

647
00:28:16,640 --> 00:28:18,119
brushes and ink, clothing,

648
00:28:18,119 --> 00:28:19,280
carriage and servants,

649
00:28:19,280 --> 00:28:20,439
I've prepared them all for you already.

650
00:28:20,680 --> 00:28:21,800
Early tomorrow, the whole family

651
00:28:21,800 --> 00:28:23,520
will send you off to the exam yard.

652
00:28:23,680 --> 00:28:25,040
Won't that be nice?

653
00:28:25,400 --> 00:28:26,920
If he wants to go, let him go.

654
00:28:30,640 --> 00:28:32,520
I was going anyway.

655
00:28:32,520 --> 00:28:33,760
You needn't chase me out, Father.

656
00:28:33,839 --> 00:28:35,359
I'm chasing you out?

657
00:28:35,800 --> 00:28:37,199
Your mother says to remain at home,

658
00:28:37,199 --> 00:28:38,199
but you insist on going to some brothel

659
00:28:38,199 --> 00:28:40,119
with your rogue friends.

660
00:28:40,400 --> 00:28:41,800
Then you say it is I chasing you out?

661
00:28:44,439 --> 00:28:46,119
Say a couple words less.

662
00:28:46,760 --> 00:28:47,280
He's going to

663
00:28:47,280 --> 00:28:48,599
the exam yard tomorrow.

664
00:28:48,719 --> 00:28:50,800
Forget it. Don't plead for him.

665
00:28:50,800 --> 00:28:51,920
He's already gone.

666
00:28:53,239 --> 00:28:54,920
How can we be the boss of him?

667
00:29:14,199 --> 00:29:15,000
Darling Second.

668
00:29:22,599 --> 00:29:24,479
Tomorrow at the exam,

669
00:29:24,479 --> 00:29:25,839
you'll surely place at the top.

670
00:29:33,199 --> 00:29:34,560
For you and the sake of the two children,

671
00:29:35,160 --> 00:29:36,520
I must pass with high marks.

672
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:39,680
You are the

673
00:29:39,680 --> 00:29:41,280
mountain for my children and I.

674
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:43,599
With you,

675
00:29:43,599 --> 00:29:44,920
I fear nothing.

676
00:29:53,599 --> 00:29:54,479
Here.

677
00:29:59,319 --> 00:30:01,719
Tonight,

678
00:30:01,719 --> 00:30:04,040
just stay in my room and don't leave.

679
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:08,400
The two children are already asleep.

680
00:30:09,280 --> 00:30:11,719
They are with the nanny. It's no trouble.

681
00:30:15,479 --> 00:30:17,359
Ye'er!

682
00:30:17,359 --> 00:30:18,839
You've got the big exam tomorrow!

683
00:30:19,239 --> 00:30:20,560
Tonight, you should drink less alcohol.

684
00:30:20,839 --> 00:30:22,479
Yes, Nanny.

685
00:30:22,479 --> 00:30:24,160
I'll go over to the study to sleep soon.

686
00:30:29,520 --> 00:30:31,520
Tomorrow,

687
00:30:31,520 --> 00:30:33,359
I'll escort you to the exam yard.

688
00:30:33,760 --> 00:30:36,239
I'll chant and pray for you outside.

689
00:30:37,199 --> 00:30:38,680
Woman, you can still chant

690
00:30:38,680 --> 00:30:40,640
and pray for him at home.

691
00:30:40,839 --> 00:30:42,760
And you've got the two children

692
00:30:42,760 --> 00:30:43,839
with no one watching them.

693
00:30:44,119 --> 00:30:45,280
Once Ye'er enters the exam yard,

694
00:30:45,280 --> 00:30:46,439
he should have nothing weighing on his mind.

695
00:30:46,680 --> 00:30:48,479
You shouldn't distract him.

696
00:30:50,479 --> 00:30:51,880
Nanny is right.

697
00:30:53,199 --> 00:30:54,680
Those restless ones in my family,

698
00:30:54,839 --> 00:30:55,959
they're looking for you everywhere,

699
00:30:55,959 --> 00:30:57,079
wanting to seize something against me.

700
00:30:57,560 --> 00:30:59,160
You must not go tomorrow for sure.

701
00:31:05,280 --> 00:31:06,280
Darling Second!

702
00:31:09,880 --> 00:31:11,560
After you pass the exam with top marks,

703
00:31:12,959 --> 00:31:14,199
you won't just abandon me, right?

704
00:31:21,479 --> 00:31:23,119
For you and the two children,

705
00:31:23,439 --> 00:31:24,719
I've already gone to a deadlock with my family.

706
00:31:25,119 --> 00:31:25,760
If I stop here

707
00:31:25,760 --> 00:31:26,760
in the middle of it,

708
00:31:26,959 --> 00:31:28,400
then the sufferings will have been in vain.

709
00:31:29,839 --> 00:31:31,160
My maternal grandfather was a merchant.

710
00:31:31,800 --> 00:31:33,119
Since I was young,

711
00:31:33,119 --> 00:31:35,359
I've known not to engage in a losing deal.

712
00:31:57,760 --> 00:31:59,160
The four writing utensils are in this box.

713
00:32:00,000 --> 00:32:00,680
The ink and tray

714
00:32:00,680 --> 00:32:01,680
are wrapped in oiled paper.

715
00:32:02,319 --> 00:32:03,560
Please be careful when you open the oiled paper,

716
00:32:03,640 --> 00:32:05,680
so you don't soil your hands.

717
00:32:06,000 --> 00:32:07,199
If ink taints the exam paper,

718
00:32:07,199 --> 00:32:08,119
that's a big trouble.

719
00:32:10,599 --> 00:32:11,439
Sixth Miss of Sheng Family,

720
00:32:11,439 --> 00:32:12,280
after taking the hare brush,

721
00:32:13,040 --> 00:32:14,040
did she send word with you?

722
00:32:15,040 --> 00:32:16,520
She just tipped me a few coins

723
00:32:16,520 --> 00:32:17,800
and took a few little items.

724
00:32:19,119 --> 00:32:20,040
She said to thank the Young Lord

725
00:32:20,040 --> 00:32:21,119
on her behalf

726
00:32:21,319 --> 00:32:22,199
and nothing else.

727
00:32:23,599 --> 00:32:24,719
Think it through again.

728
00:32:24,959 --> 00:32:26,439
I didn't even see the Sixth Miss in person.

729
00:32:26,920 --> 00:32:28,040
Even if she wanted to tell you something

730
00:32:28,040 --> 00:32:28,880
she didn't have a way to send it with me.

731
00:32:37,319 --> 00:32:39,400
That sewing shop is quite diligent.

732
00:32:39,880 --> 00:32:41,640
I told them to make two pairs of knee guards

733
00:32:41,640 --> 00:32:42,760
and he shoved an extra pair in for me.

734
00:32:43,160 --> 00:32:44,400
They even used velvet for it.

735
00:32:45,040 --> 00:32:46,959
That old sewing shop sure knows to flatter.

736
00:33:06,920 --> 00:33:08,040
"Yuanbao".

737
00:33:13,880 --> 00:33:15,199
Yuanruo.

738
00:33:16,520 --> 00:33:17,319
Let me ask you something.

739
00:33:17,680 --> 00:33:18,800
After you received the knee guards

740
00:33:18,800 --> 00:33:19,439
where did you place them?

741
00:33:19,599 --> 00:33:20,680
I put them in the basket.

742
00:33:21,199 --> 00:33:22,319
Other than the knee guards

743
00:33:22,319 --> 00:33:23,000
I also bought brushes

744
00:33:23,000 --> 00:33:24,160
ink and trays.

745
00:33:24,319 --> 00:33:25,719
I put them all in the basket.

746
00:33:25,719 --> 00:33:26,760
I sent them to Sheng House

747
00:33:26,760 --> 00:33:27,760
for Sixth Miss to pick out items

748
00:33:27,760 --> 00:33:29,920
and then brought them back.

749
00:33:32,239 --> 00:33:34,280
What are you smiling about, Young Lord?

750
00:33:40,839 --> 00:33:42,760
She has me in her heart.

751
00:33:44,439 --> 00:33:46,439
She does have me in her heart.

752
00:34:24,919 --> 00:34:26,439
Miss, I hear,

753
00:34:26,840 --> 00:34:27,760
Duke Qi rented the biggest inn

754
00:34:27,760 --> 00:34:29,280
on this street.

755
00:34:29,520 --> 00:34:30,439
What exam-taking is this?

756
00:34:30,439 --> 00:34:31,840
It's like celebrating.

757
00:34:32,919 --> 00:34:33,600
Don't talk nonsense.

758
00:34:33,639 --> 00:34:34,520
Matters of Duke Qi House

759
00:34:34,600 --> 00:34:35,879
