764
00:35:01,719 --> 00:35:03,520
the most lately.

765
00:35:04,080 --> 00:35:06,399
His family is so grand

766
00:35:06,399 --> 00:35:07,439
beyond the speakable.

767
00:35:15,280 --> 00:35:16,159
That's true.

768
00:35:16,159 --> 00:35:18,199
So it just shows that one needs to have a mother

769
00:35:18,199 --> 00:35:19,399
who is the proper wife to be the best.

770
00:35:44,959 --> 00:35:45,760
It's nearly time.

771
00:35:45,760 --> 00:35:47,879
Let them go in so they don't miss the exam time.

772
00:35:48,679 --> 00:35:50,159
May you two brothers place in the top,

773
00:35:50,159 --> 00:35:50,919
success with one stroke!

774
00:35:52,760 --> 00:35:54,760
May you two leap over the Dragon Gate

775
00:35:54,840 --> 00:35:56,120
and pluck from the Toad Palace.

776
00:35:57,120 --> 00:35:58,560
Then I may you two…

777
00:35:58,560 --> 00:36:00,879
drink lots of water and rest a lot

778
00:36:00,879 --> 00:36:02,760
during the period of exams.

779
00:36:03,959 --> 00:36:05,239
What's that you're saying?

780
00:36:06,560 --> 00:36:07,600
You don't know how to say anything auspicious?

781
00:36:08,439 --> 00:36:09,840
I just said what came to my mind.

782
00:36:10,199 --> 00:36:11,560
Then, I'll say . . .

783
00:36:12,560 --> 00:36:13,639
Two brothers,

784
00:36:13,639 --> 00:36:15,479
it must be stuffy and tiring at the exam yard,

785
00:36:15,959 --> 00:36:16,879
and water can kill the fire.

786
00:36:17,239 --> 00:36:18,360
Once your mood is better

787
00:36:18,360 --> 00:36:19,840
your essays will be written nice and pretty,

788
00:36:19,959 --> 00:36:20,840
as though helped by the divine.

789
00:36:21,040 --> 00:36:22,959
Sixth Sister's words are true.

790
00:36:22,959 --> 00:36:25,879
We shall both drink a lot of water.

791
00:36:27,919 --> 00:36:29,479
You never like to smile

792
00:36:29,479 --> 00:36:30,600
but you actually smiled, Second Brother.

793
00:36:31,199 --> 00:36:33,639
Then, let us borrow Sixth Sister's great words.

794
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:34,719
Done talking?

795
00:36:35,919 --> 00:36:36,600
Go on.

796
00:37:10,560 --> 00:37:11,679
Isn't that the Second Young Master

797
00:37:11,679 --> 00:37:12,719
of Marquis Gu Manor?

798
00:37:13,560 --> 00:37:15,320
How come he doesn't even have a carriage?

799
00:37:15,840 --> 00:37:17,120
He's the one with least fanfare.

800
00:37:20,719 --> 00:37:22,439
If that Young Master wants to grab the attention,

801
00:37:23,159 --> 00:37:24,919
I fear even the ducal manor can't cover it.

802
00:37:41,520 --> 00:37:43,000
The courtyard is locked for three days during the exam period.

803
00:37:43,280 --> 00:37:45,600
No one unrelated is allowed entrance.

804
00:37:45,760 --> 00:37:47,560
Within a hundred steps outside the exam yard,

805
00:37:47,760 --> 00:37:49,239
no one related is allowed to loiter!

806
00:37:56,919 --> 00:37:57,479
Over there.

807
00:38:15,280 --> 00:38:15,959
This?

808
00:38:24,560 --> 00:38:25,679
Confucius stated one should not

809
00:38:25,679 --> 00:38:27,879
rely on devils or illicit gods.

810
00:38:28,080 --> 00:38:29,479
You've got three gods you're praying to.

811
00:38:29,560 --> 00:38:31,399
Which one are you pleading to?

812
00:38:32,199 --> 00:38:33,879
Too much oil doesn't ruin a dish

813
00:38:33,879 --> 00:38:35,280
and too much cordiality won't ruin a person.

814
00:38:35,760 --> 00:38:37,439
Don't worry about which god.

815
00:38:37,439 --> 00:38:39,320
Just as long as I offer more incense,

816
00:38:39,560 --> 00:38:41,399
they will watch over our Changbai naturally!

817
00:38:41,840 --> 00:38:43,320
If Changbai is truly talented,

818
00:38:43,320 --> 00:38:44,280
he will pass the exam for sure.

819
00:38:44,600 --> 00:38:45,280
If he's just

820
00:38:45,280 --> 00:38:46,360
an ignorant fool,

821
00:38:46,439 --> 00:38:48,159
even if you go to Buddhist realm,

822
00:38:48,560 --> 00:38:50,320
and kneel before the Buddha himself,

823
00:38:50,320 --> 00:38:51,560
that's still useless.

824
00:38:51,959 --> 00:38:54,600
Useless or not, at least I've offered my sincerity.

825
00:38:54,879 --> 00:38:56,399
Look at Duke Qi and the wife.

826
00:38:56,600 --> 00:38:57,679
They even went to Daxiangguo Temple

827
00:38:57,679 --> 00:38:58,679
to burn incense

828
00:38:58,919 --> 00:39:00,879
and donated thousands of taels for fragrant oil.

829
00:39:01,399 --> 00:39:02,239
I am just praying to gods at home

830
00:39:02,239 --> 00:39:02,879
and nothing extravagant,

831
00:39:02,879 --> 00:39:04,479
and this still won't do?

832
00:39:06,800 --> 00:39:09,120
Minister, you come and pray too.

833
00:39:10,120 --> 00:39:11,199
Pray.

834
00:39:11,199 --> 00:39:12,120
I'm not praying.

835
00:39:12,479 --> 00:39:13,479
I told you...

836
00:39:13,479 --> 00:39:15,000
Do we keep these things you don't want

837
00:39:15,000 --> 00:39:16,360
for Second Brother?

838
00:39:16,679 --> 00:39:17,399
Let me see.

839
00:39:17,600 --> 00:39:19,120
You pray now.

840
00:39:19,120 --> 00:39:20,360
Go on.

841
00:39:31,679 --> 00:39:33,360
Dear various gods,

842
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:35,199
watch over my sons, Changfeng, Changbai,

843
00:39:35,239 --> 00:39:37,000
so they pass with high marks on the first try.

844
00:39:37,600 --> 00:39:38,760
Let our Sheng family honor our ancestors

845
00:39:38,760 --> 00:39:39,560
and bring glory to the clan.

846
00:39:40,479 --> 00:39:42,479
May the divine spirits watch over the Sheng clan.

847
00:39:50,439 --> 00:39:53,040
Minister, just pray already.

848
00:39:53,199 --> 00:39:54,840
For your son, it's nothing bad.

849
00:39:54,919 --> 00:39:56,800
Go on. Pray what?

850
00:39:57,520 --> 00:39:58,600
I have work to do.

851
00:40:37,719 --> 00:40:38,760
Why don't you eat?

852
00:40:40,639 --> 00:40:42,879
Second Son is taking the test.

853
00:40:42,879 --> 00:40:43,600
I made a wish.

854
00:40:44,479 --> 00:40:45,360
I'm abstaining from baths

855
00:40:45,360 --> 00:40:46,719
and burning incense to pray for blessing.

856
00:40:47,280 --> 00:40:48,879
I only eat two meals a day.

857
00:40:51,360 --> 00:40:52,719
You've already spoiled him rotten.

858
00:40:54,080 --> 00:40:55,000
Even if you treat him even better,

859
00:40:55,000 --> 00:40:56,159
he still won't shine.

860
00:40:57,639 --> 00:40:59,360
He's only a child still.

861
00:41:00,479 --> 00:41:01,959
No matter how he wrongs,

862
00:41:02,520 --> 00:41:03,040
I will still,

863
00:41:03,040 --> 00:41:04,320
on Sister Bai's behalf,

864
00:41:04,760 --> 00:41:05,879
dote on him more.

865
00:41:06,840 --> 00:41:07,959
Minister, don't nitpick

866
00:41:07,959 --> 00:41:08,800
with that child either.

867
00:41:10,639 --> 00:41:11,479
When others go to the exam yard,

868
00:41:11,479 --> 00:41:12,840
they call out and embrace.

869
00:41:13,520 --> 00:41:14,639
But he went without

870
00:41:14,639 --> 00:41:15,439
as much as a notice.

871
00:41:16,520 --> 00:41:17,800
How does he regard

872
00:41:17,800 --> 00:41:18,719
this father of his?

873
00:41:22,199 --> 00:41:23,479
I imagine it's because Second Son

874
00:41:23,479 --> 00:41:24,520
is worried you'd might worry

875
00:41:25,520 --> 00:41:26,439
he didn't want to call any attention to it.

876
00:41:27,439 --> 00:41:28,959
It's not like you don't know

877
00:41:28,959 --> 00:41:31,600
that child is always so thoughtful.

878
00:41:31,919 --> 00:41:32,919
Ji Kang and Ruan Ji,

879
00:41:32,919 --> 00:41:34,560
these great literary scholars.

880
00:41:35,000 --> 00:41:37,159
Which one wasn't poetic and passionate?

881
00:41:38,280 --> 00:41:40,760
Not like you. So just like him be.

882
00:41:41,760 --> 00:41:43,120
Just a petty son and how can he

883
00:41:43,120 --> 00:41:45,560
be compared to Masters Ji and Ruan?

884
00:41:46,239 --> 00:41:47,919
Don't speak for him.

885
00:41:48,360 --> 00:41:49,679
Since he passed the preliminary

886
00:41:49,679 --> 00:41:50,760
to make it to the exam,

887
00:41:50,919 --> 00:41:52,479
I'll be easy on him for a few days.

888
00:41:52,959 --> 00:41:54,840
After the exam, I'll deal with him.

889
00:41:57,600 --> 00:42:00,560
Try this. I made this especially for you.

890
00:42:06,679 --> 00:42:07,719
Hurry and eat.

891
00:42:09,679 --> 00:42:11,280
Little chicken eats rice gain.

892
00:42:17,280 --> 00:42:18,560
Feed it slowly.

893
00:42:19,800 --> 00:42:21,479
And a big bean.

894
00:42:23,719 --> 00:42:24,760
Good.

895
00:42:24,760 --> 00:42:26,399
Play well at home with Nanny.

896
00:42:27,719 --> 00:42:28,439
Where are you going?

897
00:42:31,080 --> 00:42:33,159
I just feel anxious.

898
00:42:33,520 --> 00:42:34,919
So I wanted to go to the temple

899
00:42:34,919 --> 00:42:36,439
and pray for Second Young Master.

900
00:42:37,600 --> 00:42:39,639
What did he say before he went out?

901
00:42:40,239 --> 00:42:41,560
He asked you to stay at home

902
00:42:41,560 --> 00:42:42,479
to take good care of the children,

903
00:42:42,479 --> 00:42:43,560
and not to show your face.

904
00:42:43,959 --> 00:42:44,879
So you don't get discovered

905
00:42:44,879 --> 00:42:45,719
by people from Gu House.

906
00:42:46,600 --> 00:42:48,399
Go back.

907
00:42:48,399 --> 00:42:50,600
These few exam days, you just stay home.

908
00:43:08,479 --> 00:43:09,760
Put the rice in.
